OL,3,CKiller of 9-year old Alfie Steele
OL,4,Ccan't appeal against conviction,
OL,5,Cjudges say
OL,7,FWarning: This article contains details
OL,8,Fof child abuse
OL,10,FCourt of Appeal judges have ruled that
OL,11,Fa man who was given a life sentence
OL,12,Ffor the murder of a nine-year-old boy,
OL,13,Fcannot appeal against his conviction.
OL,15,FDirk Howell was jailed for at least 32
OL,16,Fyears after a jury convicted him of
OL,17,Fkilling his partner's son Alfie
OL,18,FSteele, who was repeatedly beaten and
OL,19,Fheld down in a cold bath in
OL,20,FWorcestershire.
