OL,3,CKiller of 9-year old Alfie Steele
OL,4,Ccan't appeal against conviction,
OL,5,Cjudges say
OL,7,FAlfie died on February 18th 2021 after
OL,8,Fbeing found with 50 injuries all over
OL,9,Fhis body.
OL,11,FHe was hit with a leather belt and
OL,12,F"dunked" in the bath at his home in
OL,13,FDroitwich.
OL,15,FAlfie's mother, Carla Scott, was found
OL,16,Fguilty of manslaughter and child
OL,17,Fcruelty, while Howell was convicted of
OL,18,Fmurder.
