OL,3,CKiller of 9-year old Alfie Steele
OL,4,Ccan't appeal against conviction,
OL,5,Cjudges say
OL,7,FThe six-week trial was told that Alfie
OL,8,Fwas denied food as an act of cruelty
OL,9,Fand routinely subjected to other
OL,10,F"sinister" punishments, including
OL,11,Fbeing locked outside his Vashon Drive
OL,12,Fhome in cold weather, and made to
OL,13,Fstand in a statue-like pose.
OL,15,FWhile passing sentence at Coventry
OL,16,FCrown Court in June 2023, Mr Justice
OL,17,FWall said Howell had claimed Alfie had
OL,18,Fsuffered an epileptic fit and fallen
OL,19,Fasleep in the bath.
