OL,3,CKiller of 9-year old Alfie Steele
OL,4,Ccan't appeal against conviction,
OL,5,Cjudges say
OL,7,FAt the Court of Appeal in London today
OL,8,F(5th November), Lord Justice Green
OL,9,Fsaid Howell wanted to appeal against
OL,10,Fhis conviction on the basis that the
OL,11,Fcause of Alfie's death "could not be
OL,12,Fascertained" and that epilepsy "could
OL,13,Fnot be ruled out".
OL,15,FThe judges also said Howell had
OL,16,Fclaimed there were "corrupt payments"
OL,17,Fbetween the police and carers, while
OL,18,Fhis barristers had "improperly and
OL,19,Funfairly" represented him.
