OL,5,Cjudges say
OL,7,FThey added that these claims were
OL,8,Frejected by a previous Court of Appeal
OL,9,Fjudge who said the issues had been
OL,10,F"squarely canvassed by the jury".
OL,12,FLord Justice Green said: "We
OL,13,Funreservedly agree with the
OL,14,Fconclusions of the single judge that
OL,15,Fthe grounds for appeal are unarguable.
OL,17,F"The application for permission to
OL,18,Fappeal is refused."
