OL,3,CKiller of 9-year old Alfie Steele
OL,4,Ccan't appeal against conviction,
OL,5,Cjudges say
OL,7,FThe Worcestershire Safeguarding
OL,8,FChildren's Partnership report
OL,9,Fpublished in January this year said
OL,10,Fprofessionals from a number of
OL,11,Fagencies were involved with the family
OL,12,F"over an extended period of time".
OL,14,FThe report reviewed professional
OL,15,Finvolvement with the family from 2018,
OL,16,Fhighlighting events of drug use, abuse
OL,17,Fand neglect.
OL,19,FA mandatory referral was made to the
OL,20,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,21,F(IOPC) after the court case finished.
